.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Connect to a VM via nc
.sp
\fBWARNING:\fP
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
This requires the VM to have the selected port reverse NAT\(aqed to the host in its NAT network configuration.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
